<eesti>Seaduse rakendamine ja j&otilde;ustumine </eesti>
<inglise>Implementation and entry into force of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kuni k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel antavate &otilde;igusaktide j&otilde;ustumiseni juhindutakse tehnilise j&auml;relevalve teostamisel varem kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktidest niiv&otilde;rd, kuiv&otilde;rd need ei ole vastuolus k&auml;esoleva seadusega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Until the entry into force of legislation established on the basis of this Act, technical supervision shall be governed by legislation established earlier in so far as such legislation is not contrary to this Act. (2) This Act enters into force on 1 December 1998. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 1998. aasta 1. detsembril. </eesti>
